item.description:
Come out for our last summer meetup- It's a big fenced in park at Brookline Avenue across from Brookline Ice and Coal. How about 10:am??? I will try to call the parks dept to make sure that there is not a baseball team there. If there is one, then we will change the meetup place to Amory and I will let everyone know. Please note the Brookline AVe Park is right on Brookline Ave. Amory is at Amory and Thatcher Street. For some reason the last email had them mixed up!
Faith
